1     A 0.196 0.883 0.125  0.353 -1.805 2.402    -         -     -          -
2     B 0.022 0.914 0.129 -0.042 -2.215 2.173    -         -     -          -
  n.total n.missing n.unique
1      50         0       50
2      50         0       50

Note: mode not reported because all values of y are unique
